Webpack is a bundling tool and reduces the amount of http request.

as a normal ts setup, we get multiple HTTP request.
Installing Webpack:
npm install --save-dev webpack webpack-cli webpack-dev-server typescript ts-loader

  "devDependencies": {
    "lite-server": "^2.6.1",
    "ts-loader": "^9.2.6",
    "typescript": "^4.4.3",
    "webpack": "^5.57.1", // for bundling
    "webpack-cli": "^4.9.0",
    "webpack-dev-server": "^4.3.1"
  }